    <div class="idx"><span class="idx__t">Page review &amp; standards</span><span class="idx__rule"></span></div>
    <h2 class="h2" style="max-width:24ch;margin-bottom:18px;">Reviewed by the TechBrot Certified ProAdvisor team.</h2>
    <div class="byline">
      <div class="byline__mark" aria-hidden="true" style="background:var(--color-accent);"></div>
      <div>
        <p class="byline__name">By the Certified QuickBooks ProAdvisor team</p>
        <p class="byline__review">TechBrot Inc. &middot; Independent Certified QuickBooks ProAdvisor firm</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="prose" style="margin-top:22px;">
      <p>This page reflects how TechBrot handles Pennsylvania small-business engagements. It is maintained by the Certified QuickBooks ProAdvisor team at <strong>TechBrot Inc.</strong>, a Delaware-incorporated independent ProAdvisor firm serving Pennsylvania businesses remotely across all 67 counties, and reviewed for accuracy on the bookkeeping scope, the entity-aware chart of accounts, and the Pennsylvania references (the flat 3.07% <a href="https://www.pa.gov/agencies/revenue/" rel="noopener nofollow">personal income tax</a>, the <a href="https://dced.pa.gov/local-government/local-income-tax-information/" rel="noopener nofollow">Act 32 local Earned Income Tax</a>, and the 6% / 7% / 8% sales tax). TechBrot keeps the books and coordinates with your CPA, who files; we do not file Pennsylvania or federal returns, the local EIT return, the Local Services Tax, or Philadelphia&rsquo;s city-tax returns, and do not represent clients before the tax authorities.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="trust-row">
      {%- for c in reviewCreds %}
      <div class="trust-row__item"><p class="trust-row__value">{{ c.label }}</p><p class="trust-row__label">{{ c.detail | safe }}</p></div>
      {%- if not loop.last %}<div class="trust-row__divider"></div>{%- endif %}
      {%- endfor %}
    </div>
    <p class="meta-reviewed"><span>Published: 2026-06-26</span><span>Updated: 2026-06-26</span><span>Reviewed: 2026-06-26 &middot; Certified QuickBooks ProAdvisor</span></p>
  </div>
</section>
